          "reviewBody": "We really appreciate the hard work of all the teachers and Staff of MKNS.\nMy child is studying in school, I am very satisfied by seeing improvement and remarkable confidence level in my child's overall personality development, speaking skills and physical activity. I like the teaching system of The school where focus is given on less child student teacher ratio. I would like to extend my gratitude towards School and also wish and hope that these extended efforts would continue ....",
