            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Mansukhbhai Kothari National  School  located in Kondhwa is an exceptionally  good school. The teachers are well trained  and always strive to work for the betterment  of their children. The school focuses on adopting  new pedagogical to engage  students  actively  in the teaching  learning  process. The Anandvan initiative adopted by the school  speaks volume about its culture  and ethos..\nOverall an amazing school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
