            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My brother is studying in this school from last 8 years... He really love this school.. Teachers are very helpful and humble.. There have many extra-curriculum activities\nThis school is great.. Teachers are helpful and caring..principal is also very strict which makes the student obedient ..In manskukh bhai kothari national school they have many other activities like sports day.. English week... Speech... Etc... They also celebrated navratri nd i was invited nd it was lovely being there.. During this pandemic also the classes are going on....they have online classes....and to be honest teachers are very helpful...Teachers in this school are also very caring.. My brother was sick one day soo immediately he was taken to their clinic and he was sent home.   Teachers always keep parents updated which i really like... And teachers are very humble.... They organize many sports program so that students always feel fresh and healthy...Teachers also encourage students alot... One thing i love about MANSUKH BHAI KOTHARI NATIONAL SCHOOL is they keep students busy... I went to their school fro science exhibition and it was lovelyy... It was lovely opportunity to be over there and see how well they have moulded students... My brother always keep bragging abt school that i love 1 thing about MANSUKH BHAI KOTHARI NATIONAL SCHOOL IS sports even aftr school students who r interested in sports they have classes which i think is very supportive ...I am also going to be a teacher soon.. Would love to work in MANUKH BHAI KOTHARI NATIONAL SCHOOL",
